{"data":{"event":{"_sys":{"filename":"20240925_Oneshot","basename":"20240925_Oneshot.mdx","hasReferences":false,"breadcrumbs":["20240925_Oneshot"],"path":"content/event/20240925_Oneshot.mdx","relativePath":"20240925_Oneshot.mdx","extension":".mdx"},"id":"content/event/20240925_Oneshot.mdx","__typename":"Event","title":"One-shot Night","date":"2024-09-24T22:00:00.000Z","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Presented to you by DMs from both our community and Tarragon, we're happy to announce our first series of one-shots this year!"}]},{"type":"h4","children":[{"type":"text","text":"What are one-shots?"}]},{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"A one-shot is a short DnD story that is played in a single night, rather than the many weeks, or even months, that a full DnD campaign would take. These are excellent for getting a taste for the game or trying out a new character."}]},{"type":"h4","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Signing up"}]},{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Signing up for a one-shot happens through "},{"type":"a","url":"https://discord.com/invite/TjDUu2Gkag","title":null,"children":[{"type":"text","text":"Discord"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and will be opened next week."}]},{"type":"h4","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Hosting your own one-shot"}]},{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"If you're a DM interested in hosting a one-shot of your own, contact Brenainn (@rayningjesus) on Discord and if there are still spots available, he'll schedule you in."}]},{"type":"h2","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Planned one-shots:"}]},{"type":"h3","children":[{"type":"text","text":"The Delian Tomb"}]},{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"A group of adventurers are asked to save the blacksmith's daughter from a nearby tomb defended by goblins."}]},{"type":"ul","children":[{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"S"},{"type":"text","text":"ystem","bold":true},{"type":"text","text":": DnD 5e"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Maximum players","bold":true},{"type":"text","text":": 4 players"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Player level:","bold":true},{"type":"text","text":" 1"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Character sheets:","bold":true},{"type":"text","text":" Semi-filled, will help new players fill in the remaining details and explain character creation."}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Duration:","bold":true},{"type":"text","text":" 1 hour, and an additional 20 minutes for the character creation."}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"When:","bold":true},{"type":"text","text":" 19h- 20h20 and 20h30 - 22h"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags: Short, beginner friendly"}]}]}]},{"type":"h3","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Dead House"}]},{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Step into the foreboding world of Barovia and explore a desolated and decaying mansion where shadows twist and whispers linger in the air. Find the secrets of this once grandiose mansion. And try not to die, will you?"}]},{"type":"ul","children":[{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"System: DnD 5e"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Maximum players:  4"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Character sheets: Premade characters"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Player level: 3"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Time: 19h - 22h"}]}]}]},{"type":"h3","children":[{"type":"text","text":"The Aegis Initiative"}]},{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Brave adventurers wanted!"}]},{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Are you smart, cunning, brave or all three?"}]},{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Do you want to help make the world a better place and earn money doing so?"}]},{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"If you answered yes, then don't hestitate to head over to the Aegis Initiative on the Crystal Isle to undertake the initiative trial!"}]},{"type":"ul","children":[{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"System: DnD 5e"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Maximum players:  4"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Character sheets: Bring your own!"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Player level: 3"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Time: 20h"}]}]}]},{"type":"h3","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Charting the Dread Expanse"}]},{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"A group of adventurers arrive at a new unexplored continent to join a cartographer guild, tasked to explore an ominous, dreary and dusty region."}]},{"type":"ul","children":[{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"System: DnD 5e"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Maximum players:  4"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Character sheets: Will help people with character creation half an hour before the start of the one-shot. Backup premade sheets will be available."}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Player level: 2"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Time: 19h - 23h"}]}]}]},{"type":"h3","children":[{"type":"text","text":"The Hunt"}]},{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Calling all adventurers! A Great Beast has been spotted outside Sola’s Bastion and the militia needs help hunting it down. The Saint, blessed be their name, has put a bounty of 10,000 gold pieces on the creature’s head. Additionally, should you successfully take the creature down, you are allowed to claim one part of the Beast’s body as a trophy."}]},{"type":"ul","children":[{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"System: DnD 5e"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Maximum players:  6"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Character sheets: Premade sheets"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Player level: 3"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Time: 19h - 20h45 and 21h - 22h45"}]}]}]},{"type":"h3","children":[{"type":"text","text":"The Jacket"}]},{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Embrace the outskirts of Night City in this short adventure taking place after the events of the Cyberpunk: Edgerunners anime (viewing not required)."}]},{"type":"ul","children":[{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"System: Cyberpunk RED"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Maximum players:  5"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Character sheets: Premade sheets with set roles"}]}]},{"type":"li","children":[{"type":"lic","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Time: 18h30 - We'll see where the night takes us."}]}]}]},{"type":"p","children":[{"type":"text","text":"Sign up on "},{"type":"a","url":"https://discord.com/invite/TjDUu2Gkag","title":null,"children":[{"type":"text","text":"Discord"}]}]}]},"signupUrl":null,"groups":null}},"errors":null,"query":"\n    query event($relativePath: String!) {\n  event(relativePath: $relativePath) {\n    ... on Document {\n      _sys {\n        fi